<p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed"><li class="mb-1">Performances | Workshops | Preaching | Scripture Alive Skip to content <img src="https://scripturealive.com/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/63c952c12297d31fbe2f64b7-1-rdodoupw5xs3zetmqqhezp7qp7r859r0l2vjuexg4o.webp" alt="63c952c12297d31fbe2f64b7 (1)" class="w-full rounded-lg my-6" loading="lazy" /> Store ## Making Scripture Unforgettable ## Performances | Workshops | Speaking Invite Jeremy Refer Jeremy ## Dedicated to Proclaiming the Word with Creativity and Conviction ## Pure Scripture ## Every performance is quoted word for word from the Bible. ## Skillfully Dramatized ## A high-quality theatrical production makes Scripture leap off of the page. ## Impacting Lives ## People regularly say how moved they are and how it helps them better understand the Bible. ## Unique and Memorable ## Your audience will never forget when Scripture is dramatically presented! <img src="https://scripturealive.com/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/2107248e6e6621d6b4fe5c38c18c8cd5<em>1200</em>80-rdodoupy1h2rw6xw4mrrs0ezpy6gn7vm8zl0kghkru.webp" alt="2107248e6e6621d6b4fe5c38c18c8cd5<em>1200</em>80" class="w-full rounded-lg my-6" loading="lazy" /> <img src="https://scripturealive.com/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/7dea0315c3929177440f5d9a90340ce8<em>1200</em>80-rdodoupy1h2rw6xw4mrrs0ezpy6gn7vm8zl0kghkru.webp" alt="7dea0315c3929177440f5d9a90340ce8<em>1200</em>80" class="w-full rounded-lg my-6" loading="lazy" /> <img src="https://scripturealive.com/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/f851f13fa9d3e0e5887f74730556c3d0<em>1200</em>80-rdodoupy1h2rw6xw4mrrs0ezpy6gn7vm8zl0kghkru.webp" alt="f851f13fa9d3e0e5887f74730556c3d0<em>1200</em>80" class="w-full rounded-lg my-6" loading="lazy" /> "Jeremy transports you back in time and into the pages of Scripture. He has uncanny ability to embody all the characters in a story and keep you highly engaged. I highly recommend him when you seek to have people connect to God's Word in an entirely new way." Tami Heim, President and CEO Christian Leadership Alliance "I strongly encourage pastors and ministry leaders to utilize the ministry gifts of Jeremy Kluth. There's nothing like hearing God's Word memorized and expressed with passion. Your people will be inspired." Roy Patterson, Community Relationship Director Moody Bible Institute, Chicago IL "Jeremy has been gifted by God. Blending passion and strong contextual attention to detail, Jeremy immerses listeners' senses and emotions through his gifts of interpretive speaking. The experience brings the Word of God to life in a most memorable way." Chris Preuss, Executive Director Maranatha Bible & Missionary Conference, Muskegon MI "Scripture Alive certainly lives up to its name. Our church has walked away from Jeremy's dramatizations and workshops both in awe of the power of God's Word, and encouraged in our own walk with the Lord." Matt Vogel, Senior Pastor Grace Evangelical Free Church, Davenport IA "Jeremy Kluth is the real deal! His workshops are incredibly practical and inspiring. We loved when Jeremy did a dramatic recitation from Ezekiel in our worship service. It helped make an obscure passage click for people. It was a highlight of our series on that book." Clayton Keenon, Lead Teaching Pastor Christ Community Church, South Elgin IL "Presenting the life of the Apostle Paul entirely from the words of the Bible itself gave us all a perspective unlike anything you can experience in a sermon or topical talk. It really came alive, especially the zeal and passion within the text that are sometimes lost in our typical ways of reading them." Bob Wolniak, Senior Pastor Fulton Church, Edgerton WI "In a world lacking biblical knowledge and thirsty for truth, Scripture Alive offers an opportunity to learn and be refreshed. Jeremy Kluth is more than entertainment. He brings Scripture to life." Rick Miller, Executive Director Brethren Retreat at Shipshewana Lake, Shipshewana IN "Jeremy's high view of God and commitment to His Word have blessed and inspired our congregation to greater worship on numerous occasions through a clear expression of and careful attention to the Scriptures." Josh Beakley, Teaching Pastor Bethany Baptist Church, Edwards IL "Jeremy has strong performance skills, conviction, and a deep passion to bring God's Word to life for others. I encourage you to invite him to your conference or event to inspire and engage those you serve to follow Christ more deeply." Peter Mayberry, Vice President Awana Clubs International <img src="https://scripturealive.com/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/63c952c12297d31fbe2f64b7-1-rdodoupw5xs3zetmqqhezp7qp7r859r0l2vjuexg4o.webp" alt="63c952c12297d31fbe2f64b7 (1)" class="w-full rounded-lg my-6" loading="lazy" /> jeremy@scripturealive.com</li> </ul></p>
